\lim_{n\to\infty}\; \sqrt{n}\, \left(\sqrt{n^3+n} - \sqrt{n^3+1}\right)
\sqrt a - \sqrt b = (\sqrt a - \sqrt b)\cdot\frac{\sqrt a + \sqrt b}{\sqrt a + \sqrt b} = \frac {a - b}{\sqrt a + \sqrt b}
\begin{align} \lim_{n\to \infty}\sqrt n(\sqrt{n^3 + n} - \sqrt{n^3 + 1}) \cdot \frac{\sqrt {n^3 + n} + \sqrt{n^3 +1}}{\sqrt {n^3 + n} + \sqrt{n^3 +1}} & = \lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{\sqrt n(n - 1)}{\sqrt{n^3 + n}+ \sqrt{n^3 + 1}}\\ \\   \end{align}
n^{3/2}
 \sqrt{\vphantom{b}a}-\sqrt b=\frac{a-b}{\sqrt{\vphantom{b}a}+\sqrt b}. 
